Summary: My sister [cms pid] and I saw a UFO over the ocean when we were sitiing at the docks in Empire.
divs: Sighting DetailsWhen we were sitting at the Docks in Empire, I climbed out the window and sat on the door of her truck. We were conversing and we both saw this round object in the sky and it had lights on it. It kind of zig zigged and then like a shot was gone. We were both mesmerized and was quiet, after it was gone, we went home and told her husband about it since he used to work for the Navy and he thought we were nuts. My sister gave you a statement and I was afraid to tell you about it for fear of being called nuts, but I did see it and what she said was the truth. I hope this helps in anyway.
